<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="overflow-x:hidden">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
<title>WORDOGRAPHY — Daily Geography Puzzle</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--bg:#0D1117;--surface:#161B22;--elevated:#21262D;--border:#30363D;--text:#F0F6FC;--muted:#8B949E;--dim:#6E7681;--green:#6AAA64;--yellow:#FFB300;--grey:#3A3A3C;--amber:#E3B341;--err:#F85149;--ok:#56D364;--tile-bg:#21262D;--tile-border:#30363D;--font:Inter,sans-serif;--mono:JetBrains Mono,monospace}
[data-theme=light]{--bg:#F6F8FA;--surface:#FFFFFF;--elevated:#EAEEF2;--border:#D0D5DD;--text:#1F2328;--muted:#656D76;--dim:#8C959F;--grey:#C4C4BC;--tile-bg:#EAEEF2;--tile-border:#D0D5DD}
[data-cb=on]{--green:#58A6FF;--yellow:#F78166}
#game-content{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;width:100%}
body{font-family:var(--font);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100dvh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;user-select:none;overflow-x:hidden}
header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);gap:8px}
.header-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
h1{font-size:clamp(14px,3.8vw,19px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.5px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2EA043,#58A6FF);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
.icon-btn{background:var(--elevated);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:8px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text);font-size:15px;transition:all .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:38px;height:38px;flex-shrink:0}
.icon-btn:hover{background:var(--border)}
main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:10px 8px;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;gap:10px}
#map-canvas{border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px 10px 0 0;background:var(--elevated);display:block;max-width:100%;width:320px;height:180px}
.grid-row-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;width:100%;min-width:0;overflow:hidden;padding:0 4px}
.geo-mini{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;height:22px;margin-bottom:1px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600}
.geo-mini.revealed{opacity:1}
.geo-mini .darr{font-size:17px;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px var(--amber))}
.grid-row{display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:center}
.tile-row{display:flex;gap:5px;min-width:0;overflow:hidden}
.tile{width:calc((100vw - 36px - (var(--tl) - 1) * 5px - var(--spacers, 0px)) / var(--tl));height:calc((100vw - 36px - (var(--tl) - 1) * 5px - var(--spacers, 0px)) / var(--tl));min-width:20px;min-height:20px;border:2px solid var(--tile-border);border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;perspective:500px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:16px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--tile-bg);color:var(--text);transition:border-color .1s}.tile-spacer{width:6px;height:calc((100vw - 36px - (var(--tl) - 1) * 5px - var(--spacers, 0px)) / var(--tl));flex-shrink:0;opacity:.3;border-radius:4px;background:var(--tile-border);margin:0 2px;align-self:center}
.tile-inner{width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transform-style:preserve-3d;transition:transform .4s ease}
.tile.flip .tile-inner{animation:tileflip .4s ease forwards}
@keyframes tileflip{0%{transform:rotateX(0)}50%{transform:rotateX(90deg)}100%{transform:rotateX(180deg)}}
.tile-back{position:absolute;inset:-2px;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transform:rotateX(180deg);backface-visibility:hidden;-webkit-backface-visibility:hidden;overflow:hidden;box-sizing:border-box}
.tile-front{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;backface-visibility:hidden;-webkit-backface-visibility:hidden}
.tile.green .tile-back{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:#fff}
.tile.yellow .tile-back{background:var(--yellow);border-color:var(--yellow);color:#fff}
.tile.grey .tile-back{background:var(--grey);border-color:var(--grey);color:#fff}
.tile.green.current,.tile.yellow.current,.tile.grey.current{border-color:var(--green)}
.tile.green.flip .tile-front,.tile.yellow.flip .tile-front,.tile.grey.flip .tile-front{color:#fff}
.search-wrap{display:none}
#country-search{width:100%;padding:12px 16px;font-size:16px;font-family:var(--font);background:var(--surface);color:var(--text);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
#country-search:focus{border-color:var(--green)}
#country-search::placeholder{color:var(--dim)}
.autocomplete{position:absolute;top:calc(100%+4px);left:0;right:0;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;z-index:100;display:none;max-height:260px;overflow-y:auto;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
.autocomplete.show{display:block}
.ac-item{padding:10px 14px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:15px;transition:background .1s}
.ac-item:hover,.ac-item.active{background:var(--elevated)}
.ac-item .flag{font-size:20px}
.ac-item .cname{font-weight:500}
.ac-item .cont{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-left:auto}
.keyboard{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;width:100%;max-width:520px;margin-top:4px}
.krow{display:flex;gap:4px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.key{min-width:clamp(26px,7.2vw,40px);height:clamp(46px,11vw,56px);border:none;border-radius:6px;background:var(--elevated);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font);font-size:16px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .1s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:0 2px;touch-action:manipulation;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.key:hover{filter:brightness(1.15)}
.key.green{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
.key.yellow{background:var(--yellow);color:#fff}
.key.grey{background:var(--grey);color:#fff}
.key.wide{min-width:clamp(50px,11.5vw,70px);font-size:16px}
.key.space-key{flex:1;min-width:160px;max-width:280px;margin:0 auto}
.modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.75);z-index:200;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:16px}
.modal-overlay.show{display:flex}
.modal{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;max-width:400px;width:100%;padding:26px 22px;text-align:center;max-height:90dvh;overflow-y:auto;position:relative}
.modal .close{position:absolute;top:12px;right:14px;background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:22px;cursor:pointer;line-height:1}
.modal h2{font-size:21px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px}
.modal p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:14px}
.modal .funfact{background:var(--elevated);border-radius:10px;padding:14px;margin:12px 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--text)}
.modal .btn{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:11px 26px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);transition:opacity .15s;margin-top:8px;display:inline-block}
.modal .btn:hover{opacity:.85}
.share-grid{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;background:var(--bg);padding:12px;border-radius:8px;margin:10px 0;text-align:left;white-space:pre;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:auto}
.stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin:14px 0}
.stat-box{background:var(--elevated);border-radius:10px;padding:13px 8px;text-align:center}
.stat-box .num{font-size:26px;font-weight:800}
.stat-box .lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
.win-title{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2EA043,#56D364);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
.modal-flag{font-size:30px;margin:6px 0}
.modal-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px}
#toast{position:fixed;top:68px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px);background:var(--elevated);color:var(--text);padding:10px 20px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;z-index:300;opacity:0;transition:all .25s;pointer-events:none;border:1px solid var(--border);max-width:90vw;white-space:nowrap}
#toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}
.how-to{text-align:left;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted)}
.how-to h3{color:var(--text);margin:10px 0 4px;font-size:14px}
.how-to p{margin-bottom:8px}
.ex-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin:3px 0;font-size:12px}
.t{width:24px;height:24px;background:var(--green);border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;flex-shrink:0}
.t.y{background:var(--yellow)}
.t.g{background:var(--grey)}
.admire-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--green);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 22px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);margin-top:12px;transition:opacity .15s}
.admire-btn:hover{opacity:.85}
.already-played{display:none;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;text-align:center;padding:30px 20px}
.already-played h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px}
.already-played p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:6px}
.admire-view{display:none;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:20px;width:100%}
.admire-view.show{display:flex}
.admire-flag{font-size:48px}
.admire-country{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;margin-top:4px}
.admire-msg{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px}
.stats-row{display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.stat-chip{background:var(--elevated);border-radius:20px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.stat-chip .n{font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<div class="header-left">
<button class="icon-btn" id="help-btn" aria-label="Help">?</button>
<h1>WORDOGRAPHY</h1>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:6px">
<button class="icon-btn" id="theme-btn" aria-label="Theme">☾</button>
<button class="icon-btn" id="cb-btn" aria-label="Color blind">🔦</button>
<button class="icon-btn" id="stats-btn" aria-label="Stats">📊</button>
</div>
</header>
<main>
<div id="already-played" class="already-played" style="display:none">
  <h2>You've already played today!</h2>
  <p>Come back tomorrow for a new country!</p>
  <div class="admire-flag" id="admire-flag" style="font-size:48px;margin:16px 0"></div>
  <p id="admire-msg" style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px"></p>
  <button class="admire-btn" id="admire-btn" onclick="showAdmireView()">
    🗺️ Admire today's attempt
  </button>
</div>
<div id="game-content" style="display:none">
<div class="map-wrap">
<div style="text-align:center;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:8px">🌐 Guess The Country!</div>
<canvas id="map-canvas" width="320" height="180"></canvas>

</div>
<div class="grid-wrap" id="grid"></div>

<div class="keyboard" id="keyboard"></div>
</div>
<div id="admire-view" class="admire-view">
  <div class="admire-flag" id="admire-flag2"></div>
  <div class="admire-country" id="admire-country2"></div>
  <div id="admire-grid" class="grid-wrap"></div>
  <button class="admire-btn" onclick="hideAdmireView()" style="margin-top:8px">← Back</button>
</div>
</main>
<div id="toast"></div>
<div class="modal-overlay" id="win-modal"><div class="modal"><button class="close" aria-label="Close">×</button><div class="modal-title win-title" id="win-title"></div><p id="win-sub"></p><div class="modal-flag" id="win-flag"></div><div class="share-grid" id="win-share"></div><div class="funfact" id="win-fact"></div><button class="btn" id="win-copy">Copy Results</button></div></div>
<div class="modal-overlay" id="loss-modal"><div class="modal"><button class="close" aria-label="Close">×</button><div class="modal-title">Better luck tomorrow!</div><p id="loss-sub"></p><div class="modal-flag" id="loss-flag"></div><div class="share-grid" id="loss-share"></div><div class="funfact" id="loss-fact"></div><button class="btn" id="loss-copy">Copy Results</button></div></div>
<div class="modal-overlay" id="stats-modal"><div class="modal"><button class="close" aria-label="Close">×</button><h2>Statistics</h2><div class="stats-grid" id="stats-grid"></div><p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:10px">Avg distance: <strong id="avg-dist">—</strong></p></div></div>
<div class="modal-overlay" id="help-modal"><div class="modal"><button class="close" aria-label="Close">×</button><h2>How to Play</h2><div class="how-to"><p>Guess the <strong>hidden country</strong> in <strong>5 tries</strong>.</p><h3>Letter Feedback</h3><div class="ex-row"><div class="t">C</div><span>= correct letter, correct spot</span></div><div class="ex-row"><div class="t y">A</div><span>= correct letter, wrong spot</span></div><div class="ex-row"><div class="t g">N</div><span>= letter is not in the country</span></div><h3>Geography Feedback</h3><p>The <strong>arrow</strong> shows direction to the target. The <strong>distance</strong> shows how far away.</p><p>Press <strong>Enter</strong> or tap <strong>ENTER</strong> to submit.</p></div><button class="btn" id="help-close">Got it!</button></div></div>
<script data-v="2">
(function(){
